Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~
* numpy >= 1.0.2
* scipy >= 1.0.0
* scikit-fmm >= 1

Bugs, questions, patches, feature requests, discussion & cetera
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* Open a GitHub pull request or a GitHub issue

Installing
~~~~~~~~~~
* Via pip: `pip install scikit-traveltime`

